snippet.title: DungeonBorne: Story-based Card Game
snippet.description:
JUST RELEASED! Play DungeonBorne on your apple/android phone or tablet. https://www.Artix.com/Dungeonborne
APPLE: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/dungeonborne/id1456626814?mt=8
ANDROID: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Artix.Dungeonborne

You are a Dungeonborne, one of the brave adventurers sent by your guild to take on the Ever-Changing Dungeon! Can you survive? No, you can't. But it's lots of fun seeing how far you can get and how you die!

FEATURES
• Swipe left or right to make choices
• 4 classes to choose from
• Level up to unlock new encounters
• Play Offline. No Wifi required
• No time limit! Play till your eyes bleed!
• Free to Play!

Official website: https://www.Artix.com/DungeonBorne

Follow us on...
